Package se.martenb.iv1350.project.saleprocess.integration.dto

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddressDTO
    Represents an address.
    CustomerDTO
    Represents the customer during a sale.
    DiscountDTO
    Represents discount information after applying several discount rules.
    ItemDTO
    Represents an item in the system.
    ItemInSaleDTO
    Represents an item in a ongoing or finished sale.
    PurchaseDTO
    Represents a purchase containing the final price, amount paid and the amount of change.
    ReceiptDTO
    Represents a receipt containing information about a purchase.
    SaleDTO
    Represents an ongoing or completed sale, containing information about date/time, running total, items in sale and amount of items.
    StoreDTO
    Represents store information such as a stores' name or address.
